#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Components file for NC28 Japanese build Funai 6 hardware, NTSC or PAL display.
# Funai 6 is essentially an updated version of the Funai 4 project (modem based
#  Funai twin-smartcard hardware) OS using the new build system.
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
%Image         Build$ImageName
%Log           Build$ImageName
%Messages      Sources.Internat.Messages
%Joiner        BigSplit2
%JoinerFormat  BigSplit
%sigstr	       NCOS

